source.name: Contributors to NM Gov. Bill Richardson
source.description: For its Sept. 9, 2009 cover story, The Santa Fe Reporter used numerous public databases to determine where wealth originates in Santa Fe, NM. We then created several spread sheets. This one looks at contributors to Gov. Bill Richardson.
